Package main.java.gui

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EditRulePopup
    GUI pop-up responsible for allowing the user to edit and add different rules for visualising the excel table.
    MainFrame
    The Main Frame where the excel information is displayed and from where the user can edit and add rules, as well as calculate the code quality results
    PopupUploadFile
    This is the first frame shown to the user when initialising our tool.
    QualityRulesResultFrame
    The Code Quality Rules Results Frame will display a table with the results for running the CodeQualityRules against the methods data uploaded by the user.
